       * @deprecated since 9.9: use {@link SequenceIterator#materialize()}
       */
  
      public static <T extends Item<?>> GroundedValue<? extends T> makeSequenceExtent(SequenceIterator<T> iter) throws XPathException {
          return iter.materialize();
      }
  
